Revision history for Perl module CGI::ExceptionManager

0.06 2012-06-28

    - modernized package, use M::B instead of Module::Install.

0.05 2009-01-31

    - fixed UUV(by yappo++)

0.04 2008-12-08

    - CGI::ExceptionManager->run returns collback's return value
      or detach()'s argument

0.03 2008-11-24

    - fix generation of bogus error message when error is propagated
      from an eval (by kazuho++)

0.02 2008-11-19

    - delay load of CGI::ExceptionManager::StackTrace(by kazuho++)
    - relax parser rules (by kazuho++)

0.01 2008-11-19

    - original version

